The lovely Miriam from the Middle
East Institute has left pens for you

00:08:08.980 --> 00:08:11.260
over there, if you need a pen.

00:08:11.260 --> 00:08:16.600
So please feel free to fill the
surveys, and leave them at the desk

00:08:16.600 --> 00:08:19.300
over there at the end
of the session.

00:08:19.300 --> 00:08:23.510
So, without further
adieu, Dr. Rana Al Kadi.

